org.javafxdata.datasources.reader

Class NetworkSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javafxdata.datasources.reader.NetworkSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSourceReader
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RestRequest

    public class NetworkSource
extends Object
implements DataSourceReader
    Implementation of DataSourceReader for obtaining data from a network source (e.g. a static XML file, a dynamically served REST interface,...). Instances of this class can be created and passed in the constructor of a protocol implementations in the org.javafxdata.datasources.io package.
    Note that using this class does not create a binding between the physical network source and the view that renders the data.
    Author:
    johan
